{"tid":1400240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"八五三罷，唔好全部去曬金鐘！","createTime":"2019-08-03T11:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:58:38.000Z","uid":285539,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8648cd23cbc40c049da37bba976acc20c58961","tid":1400240,"uid":285539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"身邊好多隊友都話星期一要去金鐘發夢，因為金鐘會係主要戰場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係七區集結嘅意義係咩？就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遍地開花</span></span></span>吖嘛！等各區罷工嘅人可以去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">最方便</span></span>嘅地方集會。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家都去曬金鐘，咁其他地方就會好冷清，失去左本身搞七區集結嘅意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以，建議大家<strong>去番自己附近地方</strong>，一於迫爆七區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"575c0b3fe50a08e6d662912155a82b96cd1a0b36","tid":1400240,"uid":285539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"push！"},{"pid":"ed38645173cb5ac6ee9d618ce3d3511c62bb8796","tid":1400240,"uid":285539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04153aa20d8b0012d6d8fea44e3e273f3c4ac5f7","tid":1400240,"uid":285539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"129815b107dea1a21996a43110741662d96d9465","tid":1400240,"uid":285539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fa387dfceba5dffff0f3cae10d6a96225bfd64f","tid":1400240,"uid":249063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"